== Amir Khusrow ==

Amir Khusrovh (zolm 1253; moronn 1325).

farsi bhaxentlo namnecho bharoti-i kovi, vidvan ani songitkar. tachem purai nanv Ab'ul Hasan Yamīn ud-Dīn khusrow ( dehlovi. tacho zolm' etta jilheantolea (ut'tor prodex) pottim-ali ganvant zalo. tacho bapui omir soifud'din mohmud ho turkostanantlo sordar axil'lo. to oltomxoche mustint bhartant ievn sthaik zalo. tachi avoi bharoti-i axil'li. to dha vorsacho astonach tacho bapui bhair poddlo. tachea ajean (avoicho bapui) ani avoin taka vaddoilo. lhan astonach to nizamud'din oulia hea sotpuruxacho onuiai zalo. tachevixim khusrovk khub ador ani mog axil'lo.

tannem lhan astonach kovita boronvk survat keli toxench farsi, orbi, turki ani hindi hea bhaxancho obheas kelo. dil'lichea rajdorbarant razkovi mhunn tannem khub vorsam kam' kelem. koikubad hea sultanan taka 'molik-ux-xuora' mhollear 'kovismratt' oxi podvi dili.igannantle farsi vidvan tacho 'tuti-e-hind' (bharotacho popott) mhunn govrov kortale. tachi kavio nirmonni khub unch panvddeachi zavn asa. to farsi bhaxentlo namnecho kovi axil'loch te bhair bhaxaxastrgone, songitoar, guddhvadi ani oxttotasancho vidvan oshi tannem kirt melloili.

hindustani songitachea mollar tannem moladik vaur kelo ani tem chodd somrid'dh kelem. kaim nove rag ani mixr rag toiar korun te lokam'modim pavoilem. dekhik- iomon, koleann, kafi, bohor, zhilof, sanzgiri, mojir, forgon, sormodi adi. sotar hem vade lokam'modim pavovpachem xrei takach vota. kovali pod'dhotichi gaiki khursoin poilim sodun kaddli oxem mhonnttat. pokhovazaposun toblem ani ddoggo oxe don bhag korun tachem ek novem vade tannem toiar kelem ani procharant haddlem. taka songittgoneamni 'naik' oxi bhoumanachi podvi dil'li.

farsintlea namnechea kovim'modim tachi gonn'na zata. tachea kaveant sokhol onubhuti, kolponaxokt ani khas korun bharoti-i upma ani olonkar hancho aspav asa. tannem godio kavio legit boroilam. tatunt tachi svotontr xoili disun ieta. bharotavixim taka upatt mog axil'lo. 'nu sipihor' hea tachea gronthant tannem bhartachem ginean ani somskritai hancho bhoumanan ul'lekh kela.

tachi gronth nirmonni oxih panch kovitam jhele (divan): 1.tuhfotul-sigor (1272) 2.vostul hiat(1285) 3. gurrotul-komal (1294) 4. bokia-e-nokia (1316) ani 5. nihaitul- komal (1324). panch itihasik khonddkaveam (tarikhi mosnovim-am) o 1. kiranus-sooden (1289) 2. miftahul-futuho (1291) 3. khizror khan doul' rani(1316) 4. nu sipihor (1318) ani 5. tugsok nama(1324). him khonddkaveam razanchem ani sultanachem tustecher adaril'lim asat.

iranncho namnecho farsi kovi nizami-e-gonzvi (sumar 1141-1203) hannem 'khomsa' mhollear panch mosnovim-am boroileat, tacho adorx fuddem dovrun khusrovn 1298 te 301 hea kallant panch mosnovim-am boroileo. 1.motl u'la onvar 2. xiri khusrov 3. mojnum loila 4. aina-i-sikondori ani 5. hoxt-bihixt. tin godio gronth 1. khozainu,la futuho (ol'la- ud'din khiljichea kallcho itihas) 2. iozaje khusorvi (sfutt lekhancho jhelo) 3. ofzolu' la fovaid (nizamud'din oulia hachea vochnancho ani updexamocho jhelo).

zovahore khusorvi hea nanvacho ek kaviojhelo asun tatunt tache dohe,git, pohelim-am (kuttkavio) ani farsi-hindi bhorosl'lim kaim podam hancho aspav asa. tannem hindi bhaxentui borich gronth rochnnuk kelea oxem mhonnttat. 'khalik bori' nanvacho tacho hindi godegronth nanvajil'lo asa.


